{"tid":813923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上千退伍老兵成都維權被噴辣椒水","createTime":"2018-09-11T00:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T15:53:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a661b3111d81e9edfa0071317c8469a250b37c88","tid":813923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:14:38.000Z","msg":"上千退伍老兵成都維權被噴辣椒水<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180911&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20496961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180911%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20496961&d=CQZlTY4cDBAUj8UcafCqrKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6745c69c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180911%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20496961&h=8b28ca65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180911&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20496961</a><br />\n<br />\n內地再有大規模退伍老兵維權活動，四川成都昨有數千老兵聚集，到省政府院外請願，並與警察發生肢體衝突，一些老兵被噴辣椒水。入夜後傳有一名副省長與老兵表會談，老兵揚言，會談沒有結果，將在省政府外通宵靜坐。另一方面，北京昨有有數百老兵聚集在中央軍委信訪大院前靜坐，申訴維權。<br />\n<br />\n數百老兵北京上訪靜坐<br />\n<br />\n據Twitter上流傳多條短片所見，數以千計老兵拉起橫額或標語聚集，然後而列隊操往省政府，有的則到民政廳請願。片中出現老兵在中間走，兩邊有警察夾着他們前行，形成「維權三明治」的奇特場面。據悉，曾有四川民政廳官員曾「承諾接談」，了解老兵訴求，但最終沒有任何官員出來，警察欲驅趕老兵時，因發騷亂，雙方一度爆發衝突。昨晚9時，傳有副省長接見老兵代表，但未知商談結果，老兵們不排除將通宵在省政府外靜坐。<br />\n<br />\n「數百老兵聚集中央軍委信訪大院前，北京愛民街39號。老兵還在增加。」Twitter亦出現大批老兵聚集請願。數十名據稱來自河北的老兵，則直接挺進到中南海紅牆外聚集維權。<br />\n<br />\n近年內地發生多次退伍軍人大規模維權事件，他們不滿安置計劃難以落實，請願要求提高退休金，改善福利待遇。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/美國之音"},{"pid":"0adb5da719b8c9723f88ad95a2484929d78fe0d2","tid":813923,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入夜後傳有一名副省長與老兵表會談，老兵揚言，會談沒有結果，將在省政府外通宵靜坐。另一方面，北京昨有有數百老兵聚集在中央軍委信訪大院前靜坐，申訴維權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n當年老毛班共匪俾蔣公圍剿又係咪響南京靜坐抗議呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雜種講左喇, 不忘初心呀, 拎返D架撐起義喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b325e449d3bb5abb1874d64f7c63ad4c4e01ade","tid":813923,"uid":129043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:22:39.000Z","msg":"做咩唔用坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07aa7f361f373898e6d57d6b1edc6b2e8fcf79d0","tid":813923,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:34:06.000Z","msg":"抵能死<br />\n<br />\n快啲開槍啦"},{"pid":"d0223bacf2698b9c9f3613d145598e60c8d758f0","tid":813923,"uid":52939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"大陸唔係好撚有錢?<br />\n成日千億千億咁送比非洲<br />\n自己班老兵乞個一百幾十又唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b339aec0b242250f220d6f5019048967540d7bf","tid":813923,"uid":191738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"成千個前軍人打唔死公安？中共軍力真強"},{"pid":"93ec1597c19138911cb6f5659a45588e9aee24c0","tid":813923,"uid":15410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"為虎作悵抵撚死"},{"pid":"bb64aaf76aad7ba97966e946f9d619ddff0612b1","tid":813923,"uid":33104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"話知你係雜種，維權就要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dacbbd06e8bdfc21212b43cb56f2003324fbb0f","tid":813923,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:57:59.000Z","msg":"咁唔和平理性㗎有咩坐低慢慢傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e09dee5442fdb32fdd3d96199613a040e9969a","tid":813923,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"車下啲豬肉先啦"},{"pid":"27a0f9dd4cb7109cce19090f5c2d8f4aa35638ef","tid":813923,"uid":56321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"後生為共黨當兵，點知家陣「厲害了我的國」，臨老唔過得世<br />\n<br />\n呢班應該唔似而家班少爺兵，少爺兵比錢買位，班老兵犹真心膠"},{"pid":"d80aba0a94cf3a68e4b2980ef4d2bb456a706a04","tid":813923,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"又1扭屎忽"},{"pid":"e68ed4572e9d3fc50b98d1514653f716c3fed77f","tid":813923,"uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a0f9dd4cb7109cce19090f5c2d8f4aa35638ef","tid":813923,"uid":56321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"後生為共黨當兵，點知家陣「厲害了我的國」，臨老唔過得世<br />\n<br />\n呢班應該唔似而家班少爺兵，少爺兵比錢買位，班老兵犹真心膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"共產黨condom"},{"pid":"5f7ffbf460c079155cff51b77454f6dc02062a57","tid":813923,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"幾時坦克碌豬"},{"pid":"b6199a7ce591b5839543e8bceeaf0a33bd95277a","tid":813923,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0223bacf2698b9c9f3613d145598e60c8d758f0","tid":813923,"uid":52939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"大陸唔係好撚有錢?<br />\n成日千億千億咁送比非洲<br />\n自己班老兵乞個一百幾十又唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13